These are Puzzles for 1x3 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-4-1::.
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: lacrosse, cycling, handball
1. the person who's sport is cycling is on the right of the person who's sport is handball##1
2. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the far right##1
3. the person who's sport is lacrosse is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |       2       |   3   |
| Sport   | handball | cycling | lacrosse |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-4-2::.
There 3 different types of food: orange, kale, garlic
1. the person eating kale is in an odd position##4
2. the person eating orange is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |    1    |     2      |   3    |
| Food   | orange | garlic | kale |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-4-3::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: collecting, chess, photography
1. the person who's hobby is chess is in an even position##4
2. the person who's hobby is chess is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is photography##3
3. the person who's hobby is photography is on the right of the person who's hobby is chess##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |    2    |      3       |
| Hobby   | collecting | chess | photography |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-4-4::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: classical, r&b, reggae
1. the fan of r&b is in an odd position##4
2. the fan of reggae is on the left of the fan of r&b##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |   2    |  3   |
| Music-Genre   | classical | reggae | r&b |

